*<div id="function.openssl-get-privatekey" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">openssl_get_privatekey</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">openssl_get_privatekey</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">别名 <span class="function">{@link openssl_pkey_get_private()}</span></span></p>   </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.openssl-get-privatekey-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <p class="simpara">    此函数是该函数的别名：    <span class="function">{@link openssl_pkey_get_private()}</span>.   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.openssl.php">OpenSSL 函数</a></div></div>
