ers">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <dl>          <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">password</span></dt>      <dd>       <span>       派生密钥所生成的密码。      </span>     </dd>              <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">salt</span></dt>      <dd>       <p class="para">       PBKDF2 推荐一个不少于64位(8字节)的密码盐值。      </p>     </dd>              <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">key_length</span></dt>      <dd>       <p class="para">       希望输出密钥的长度。      </p>     </dd>              <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">iterations</span></dt>      <dd>       <p class="para">       需要的迭代次数 <a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/https://pages.nist.gov/800-63-3/sp800-63b.php#sec5" class="link external">&raquo;&nbsp;NIST        建议至少10,000次</a>.      </p>     </dd>              <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">digest_algorithm</span></dt>      <dd>       <p class="para">       在<span class="function">{@link openssl_get_md_methods()}</span>中可选的散列或摘要算法.默认是 SHA-1.      </p>     </dd>        </dl>   </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.openssl-pbkdf2-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    成功，返回原始二进制字符串 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span>FALSE</span></strong>.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.openssl-pbkdf2-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-936">     <p><strong>Example #1 openssl_pbkdf2() 范例</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$password&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'yOuR-pAs5w0rd-hERe'</span><span style="